{"tid":1545275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同你地班黑衣暴徒講幾句","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:53:03.000Z","uid":276575,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6771a394a040d5dbd430bee3708cd6b18ae60bc","tid":1545275,"uid":276575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"6月9號敲響了第一戰<br />\n6月12號我們面對了240枚催淚彈、3發布袋鉛彈、19發橡膠子彈和30發海綿彈仍然未退縮，我們昂首挺胸面迎戰。<br />\n<br />\n黑警濫暴時，我們沒有沉默，咬緊牙關堅持，<br />\n甚至有手足以死來控訴政府，<br />\n夠了，真的夠了。<br />\n<br />\n想想當十二，十三歲上前線時，<br />\n這世代為什麼逼使他們要上街？<br />\n我們更應當站起來。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，這場運動已經持續接近三個月，<br />\n有人認為政府決定動議撤回，運動亦都相繼告吹。<br />\n<br />\n不！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n一滴水滴看似簡單，沒用，<br />\n但聚集七百萬水滴就能成河！<br />\n<br />\n我地可以泄氣，但唔可以放棄。<br />\n我地可以感到絕望，但唔可以放棄希望。<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，你地生命好寶貴。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\nFight for freedom <br />\nStand with Hong Kong"},{"pid":"a755f407c46fea17cf3dff391f494df9af30690e","tid":1545275,"uid":114165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3be0943984f7cba98edf28d8cd21c8e36f080c1b","tid":1545275,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></sp